      "explanation": "O posibilă soluţie ar fi cost[1][1]*0 + cost[1][2]*4 + cost[1][3]*1 + cost[2][1]*3 + cost[2][2]*0 + cost[2][3]*3 = 5 * 0 + 2 * 4 + 3 * 1 + 5 * 3 + 3 * 0 + 4 * 3 = 38."
    }
